explanation: "Delirium tremens is treated with benzodiazepines like oxazepam, opioid overdose with naloxone, alcohol dependence maintenance with acamprosate, and smoking cessation with varenicline. Flumazenil is not used here.\n<img src=\"https://corebtr-assets-production.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/question_explanation/5d5c2d0f-66c8-4c61-b255-f41e65e10962.jpg\" alt=\"Uploaded Image\">",
