text: "Consider the following statements about behavior change stages and choose the correct answer : \n\u2022\tStatement 1: Contemplation \u2013 A person who smokes is thinking of quitting smoking.\n\u2022\tStatement 2: Precontemplation \u2013 A person is considering starting morning walk considering its benefits to health.\n\u2022\tStatement 3: Maintenance phase \u2013 A person quit smoking one year back and has not smoked since then.\n\u2022\tStatement 4: Action phase \u2013 A person with obesity says he can't do anything as it runs in his family.",
